      <title>俄罗斯向中国输送天然气日均量创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/russia-s-daily-pipeline-gas-flows-to-china-set-new-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据能源巨头俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司称，12 月 20 日，俄罗斯通过西伯利亚力量管道向中国输送的天然气日流量创下了新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/russia-s-daily-pipeline-gas-flows-to-china-set-new-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 11:25:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>绿色氢气从被大肆宣传到因成本惊人而备受冷落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/green-hydrogen-goes-from-hyped-to-humbled-on-eye-popping-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于成本下降的预期未能实现，今年大量生产绿色氢（一种被认为对于实现净零排放至关重要的燃料）的项目被放弃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/green-hydrogen-goes-from-hyped-to-humbled-on-eye-popping-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可可将成为 2024 年最大的商品赢家。一切尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/cocoa-caps-2024-as-biggest-commodity-winner-it-s-not-over-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年，可可的涨势已超越所有主要大宗商品，而且几乎没有迹象表明导致其近乎垂直的轨迹的供应紧张和脆弱的交易格局会得到快速解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/cocoa-caps-2024-as-biggest-commodity-winner-it-s-not-over-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Party City 第二次申请破产 零售业重现昔日辉煌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/party-city-files-for-bankruptcy-a-second-time-in-retail-deja-vu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Party City Holdco Inc. 在两年内第二次申请破产，并表示由于销售额在顽固的通货膨胀压力下下滑，将开始关闭其约 700 家门店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/party-city-files-for-bankruptcy-a-second-time-in-retail-deja-vu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 06:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅赛德斯明星制造商的倒闭表明汽车业的困境如何打击供应商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/mercedes-star-maker-s-demise-shows-how-auto-pain-hits-suppliers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国 Gerhardi Kunststofftechnik GmbH 公司经受住了拿破仑入侵、大萧条和两次世界大战的考验。但欧洲目前的汽车业低迷让这家塑料制造商陷入了困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/mercedes-star-maker-s-demise-shows-how-auto-pain-hits-suppliers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
